channel.title: Something weird on silabs
channel.description:
i finally got a silabserver and client that works and then:
when i have a skillcape, it looks like a dwarven face, and it is called "null"
now i changed the values to 20000 in the client.java and compiled, but, now my server is broken with this error:
[code]ClientHandler: Accepted from 127.0.0.1:50509 Exception in thread "Thread-0" java.lang.NoSuchMethodError: client.<init>(Ljava/ net/Socket;I)V at PlayerHandler.newPlayerClient(PlayerHandler.java:44) at server.run(server.java:153) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source)[/code]
